      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. I\u2019ve babied this car since the moment I got it, and it\u2019s still in absolutely pristine, showroom condition! It looks and smells brand new, with not a single mark on it. It drives like a dream and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage its whole life. I'm honestly sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to be over the moon with it. Feel free to come by and check it out\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
