    {
      "id": "sybil_26_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_26",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered legend. The 3.2L high-revving inline-six features a documented VANOS overhaul and a reinforced rear subframe, ensuring optimal structural integrity and valve timing precision. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a factory variable M-differential. The chassis remains in concours condition with zero bushing deflection and original factory tolerances throughout the suspension geometry. Featuring unblemished paintwork and a pristine undercarriage, this specimen represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance for the discerning collector.",
